Killer scientists
A group of scientists is working in the ruined mansion.  Their mission is to find out what caused the destruction, and how to harness this force as a weapon. You must stop them at all costs.
#subobj  1
Finding the ruined mansion
The ruined mansion is located in the desert north of the City of Suslanger and the surrounding irrigated fields.
#subobj  2
Killing the Scientists and Magicians
You must kill all the Scientists who conduct research and all the Warrior Magicians who guard them.
